text:
Hi,

This is not a bug, or an issue with the Apache product.
You need use of the of the support forums to get some assistance in resolving
your problem.

You can do that by looking here,
http://httpd.apache.org/docs/trunk/faq/#support.what2do

I would suggest the IRC forum for a quicker response, but the users mailing list
maybe more appropriate if your English is not very strong.

Cheers,
Tony
creator: tony@pc-tony.com

text:
This is a support question and belongs on a support channel, not the bug list.

Please send your question to the users@httpd.apache.org mailing list or the #apache channel on the 
freenode irc network, preferably with some information that might help to diagnose the problem.
